WEBVTT

00:02:58.998 --> 00:03:01.622
they beat him up in front of me,

00:03:01.622 --> 00:03:04.306
tied him, dragged him away.

00:03:05.536 --> 00:03:10.321
I was handcuffed, blindfolded,
and forced to kneel,

00:03:10.321 --> 00:03:14.204
as the silencer of a gun
pressed against my neck.

00:03:14.204 --> 00:03:15.942
When it happens to you,

00:03:15.942 --> 00:03:18.975
there is no time for thinking,
no time for praying.

00:03:20.045 --> 00:03:22.749
My brain went on automatic,

00:03:22.749 --> 00:03:27.115
rewinding quickly
the life I'd just left behind.

00:03:27.115 --> 00:03:29.645
It took me long minutes to figure out

00:03:29.645 --> 00:03:33.058
that those masked men there
were not there to kill me,